com.siperian.sif.message

Class Record

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.Record
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SiperianObjectUidProvider, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HMRecord

    public class Record
extends Object
implements SiperianObjectUidProvider, Serializable
    A row of data from an object in Siperian Hub.

    A Record consists of a list of fields and, optionally, a SiperianObjectUID.

    See Also:
    SiperianObjectType, Field, Serialized Form

      • getFieldValues

        public List getFieldValues(List columnUids)
        Parameters:
        columnUids - - List of column UIDs for which values are required. Can be null or empty.
        Returns:
        A List of values corresponding to the column UIDs. The List can be empty but never null. Objects in the returned List will be null if a column is not found in this Record.
